  "title": "Class 4 Driver",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Loading and unloading of uniforms/linens trolley at factory &amp; customer premises</li>\n  <li>Ensure correct loading of goods onto delivery vehicles</li>\n  <li>Ensure timely delivery of goods to customers</li>\n  <li>Document handling such as D/O and Invoice</li>\n  <li>Provide good customer service during delivery</li>\n  <li>Adhere to assigned routes &amp; follow time schedules</li>\n  <li>Abide by all transportation laws &amp; maintain safe driving records</li>\n  <li>Handle vehicles, equipment &amp; devices provided by company with care</li>\n  <li>Maintain basic housekeeping, cleanliness &amp; hygiene of vehicle assigned</li>\n  <li>Any other ad hoc duties assigned by supervisor/manager</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Class 4 driving License</li>\n  <li>Good attitude &amp; willing to learn</li>\n  <li>Good communication skills</li>\n  <li>Able to commit to 6 day work week schedule with rotational off days</li>\n  <li>Have basic knowledge in maintenance of vehicle</li>\n</ul>",
